feat: Add Gatling test framework with TypeScript setup

Integrated Gatling with TypeScript to enable performance testing
and report generation. Configured project structure and provided
key components for defining and running test scenarios.

Key changes:
- Added TypeScript support for Gatling.
- Defined step implementations in `src/steps` folder.
- Created simulation files with `gatling-sym` prefix for test flows.
- Configured reporting system to generate HTML reports in the `target` folder.
- Updated README with detailed instructions on running tests and project structure.

Related documentation: https://gatling.io/docs/
